body.paragraph:
‘‘Pañcimā , bhikkhave, saññā bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā honti mahānisaṃsā amatogadhā amatapariyosānā. Katamā pañca? Asubhasaññā, maraṇasaññā, ādīnavasaññā, āhāre paṭikūlasaññā, sabbaloke anabhiratasaññāanabhiratisaññā 
Note { id=0, line='3', referenceLine='3', original='anabhiratisaññā (ka.) a. ni. 5.121-122, 303-304 passitabbaṃ', type='auto', previous=', bhikkhave, saññā bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā honti mahānisaṃsā amatogadhā amatapariyosānā. Katamā pañca? Asubhasaññā, maraṇasaññā, ādīnavasaññā, āhāre paṭikūlasaññā, sabbaloke anabhiratasaññā '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='anabhiratasaññā'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='anabhiratisaññā'}}
– imā kho, bhikkhave, pañca saññā bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā honti mahānisaṃsā amatogadhā amatapariyosānā’’ti. Paṭhamaṃ.

