body.paragraph:
‘‘Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vā bhikkhunī vā pañca dhamme 
Note { id=5, line='36', referenceLine='23', original='ime pañca dhamme (ka.)', type='auto', previous=' Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vā bhikkhunī vā pañca dhamme '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='pañca dhamme'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='ime pañca dhamme'}}
bhāveti, pañca dhamme 
Note { id=6, line='45', referenceLine='23', original='ime pañca dhamme (ka.)', type='auto', previous=' bhāveti, pañca dhamme '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='pañca dhamme'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='ime pañca dhamme'}}
bahulīkaroti, tassa dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ – diṭṭheva dhamme aññā, sati vā upādisese anāgāmitā.

‘‘Katame pañca? Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, vīriyasamādhi…pe… cittasamādhi… vīmaṃsāsamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, ussoḷhiññeva pañcamiṃ 
Note { id=7, line='54', referenceLine='24', original='ussoḷhīyeva pañcamī (sī.)', type='auto', previous='Katame pañca? Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, vīriyasamādhi…pe… cittasamādhi… vīmaṃsāsamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, ussoḷhiññeva pañcamiṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='ussoḷhiññeva pañcamiṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='sī.', text='ussoḷhīyeva pañcamī'}}
. Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vā bhikkhunī vā ime pañca dhamme bhāveti, ime pañca dhamme bahulīkaroti, tassa dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ – diṭṭheva dhamme aññā, sati vā upādisese anāgāmitā’’ti. Sattamaṃ.

 ‘‘Pubbevāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sambodhā anabhisambuddho bodhisattova samāno pañca dhamme bhāvesiṃ, pañca dhamme bahulīkāsiṃbahulimakāsiṃbahulamakāsiṃ 
Note { id=8, line='63', referenceLine='26', original='bahulimakāsiṃ (ka.), bahulamakāsiṃ (ka.)', type='auto', previous=' Pubbevāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sambodhā anabhisambuddho bodhisattova samāno pañca dhamme bhāvesiṃ, pañca dhamme bahulīkāsiṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='bahulīkāsiṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='bahulimakāsiṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='bahulamakāsiṃ'}}
. Katame pañca? Chandasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāvesiṃ , vīriyasamādhi… cittasamādhi… vīmaṃsāsamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāvesiṃ, ussoḷhiññeva pañcamiṃ. So kho ahaṃ, bhikkhave, imesaṃ ussoḷhipañcamānaṃ dhammānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā yassa yassa abhiññāsacchikaraṇīyassa dhammassa cittaṃ abhininnāmesiṃ abhiññāsacchikiriyāya, tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇiṃ sati sati āyatane.

‘‘Katame pañca? Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu asubhānupassī kāye viharati, āhāre paṭikūlasaññī, sabbaloke anabhiratasaññīanabhiratisaññī 
Note { id=9, line='73', referenceLine='31', original='anabhiratisaññī (ka.) a. ni. 5.121-122, 303-304 passitabbaṃ', type='auto', previous='Katame pañca? Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu asubhānupassī kāye viharati, āhāre paṭikūlasaññī, sabbaloke anabhiratasaññī '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='anabhiratasaññī'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='anabhiratisaññī'}}
, sabbasaṅkhāresu aniccānupassī, maraṇasaññā kho panassa ajjhattaṃ sūpaṭṭhitā hoti. Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ekantanibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattantī’’ti. Navamaṃ.
